{"tid":786881,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為想買最新限量版PS4同女朋友吵交","createTime":"2018-08-20T08:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T09:13:31.000Z","uid":141869,"like":2,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"971bd8eeab1e146bfb36be20b72a1d5af64ef2ff","tid":786881,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:54:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n講返背景先，我同佢都係財政獨立<br />\n但因為一齊咗咁耐<br />\n所以我多多少少都有問佢借啲錢<br />\n加埋應該都有幾萬蚊，唔多記得了<br />\n但我每個月還完卡數min pay之後<br />\n就算再缺錢都一定會買返啲野哄佢開心<br />\n哩啲冇計啦鬼叫我咁錫佢<br />\n咁今次出限量PS4我就諗住買<br />\n個樣又靚又可以保值，咁我就同佢講<br />\n佢竟然叫我賣咗舊個部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴撚線打左咁耐有感情嫁都<br />\n我叫佢再借啲錢比我買PS4但佢話冇錢<br />\n我先至唔信<br />\n我知佢有做freelance應該搵唔小<br />\n但係佢唔肯借<br />\n我突然覺得我地之間冇咗以前個種信任<br />\n頭先同佢吵完佢喊得好西利<br />\n買PS4咁少事佢都唔支持我<br />\n我仲應唔應該再同佢一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d863ffcbf4b0274b75df5cd3a975b000556ff00c","tid":786881,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦"},{"pid":"7404e6f8d49f346e82b2e4ab8fb3c7f11236f1b8","tid":786881,"uid":13160,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"特登打咁多字扮事主咁樣好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445b9d3ca15e05ea5e01ef19bc9b6a1f3b27ff80","tid":786881,"uid":161125,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:01:06.000Z","msg":"做多左"},{"pid":"0fd3e3f5cc82ffd4ea35485759aef102c6498c8b","tid":786881,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7404e6f8d49f346e82b2e4ab8fb3c7f11236f1b8","tid":786881,"uid":13160,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"特登打咁多字扮事主咁樣好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"幾好心機....<br />\n有呼應"},{"pid":"6eafbe66a88cd878ab4b740e4ec5bc55e8dfefb8","tid":786881,"u